By the blood of House Holimion, I decree that I shall enforce the Twelve Edicts of Order, the Charter of Noble Succession, and the Covenant of the Crowned Alliance;  
I shall rely upon the High Council of Elders, the Order of the Silver Scepter, and House Verdant Crown;  
any breach shall be met with forfeiture of title, exile, and loss of privileges, for the stability of our realm depends upon the sanctity of blood and rank.
